The Department of Water and Sanitation’s Directorate: Reserve Determinations has undertaken a study of ‘Gazetting of the Reserve in the Inkomati Catchment’. More details are now available on the Government Printing bulletin for a 60 days comment process/period. It can be accessed in the Government Gazette of 10 November 2017, pages: 230-287, on the Government Printing Website under report 41237. Find the gazette here Any comments should be sent to Yakeen Atwaru (AtwaruY@dws.gov.za) or Molefi Mazibuko (MazibukoM@dws.gov.za).